<div class="container home-container">
    <h1 class="home-title">Looking to get active?</h1>
    <div>
        <p></p>Here on London Teams we're working with communities to build a database of every sports team across London's 32 boroughs, for all ages and levels.</p>
        <p><b>Find your local team and get involved!</b></p>
        <div class="container home-info">
          <div class="home-card">
            <h4>Get involved</h4>
            <p>Find a team or find a sport you might be interested using the buttons above.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="home-card">
            <h4>Add your team</h4>
            <p>Sign up now and add your team to the database!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="../images/football.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Girls playing football">
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="../images/swimming.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Child swimming">
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="../images/basketball.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Boys playing basketball">
              </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
          </div>
    </div>
</div>